name: 10th Anniversary Button Pack
description:
Limited Edition "Fondant vs. Buttercream" Button Pack!!

You get 4 buttons:

- I *heart* Fondant 
- I *heart* Buttercream
- Merci Beaucoup 10th Anniversary "X" Logo
- Merci Beaucoup 10th Anniversary "10" Logo

The Fondant & Buttercream buttons are printed on Busy Beaver Buttons "Cosmic" paper!!!  All packs are hand signed and #'d to only 50 sets.

All orders include shipping.

name: The Merci Tote Bag! *Final Quantities*
description:
Perfect for the caker on the go, this tote can hold up to rigors of a busy cake decorator!  Bring it to load up on gum paste at your favorite supply store, carry it at a convention or use it for all your tools when out on a delivery!  You can do anything with our tote!

Made of 600 denier polyester, the tote is easy to clean and has one large main compartment with an interior hanging pocket and a side pocket for organizing your stuff!  The tote is a chocolate brown and will have the Merci Beaucoup Hummingbird logo screened on one side in a lovely light aqua blue.  Dimensions: 12"h x 14"w x 6.5"d

All orders include shipping and handling!!
